data.description: This well maintained 1584 Sq. Ft. manufactured home presents an inviting open-concept floor plan. Featuring a spacious family room, a master bedroom complete with a walk-in closet and private en suite bathroom, a laundry room, and newer flooring throughout, this home is very comfortable and functionable. With recent upgrades, including a new roof, instant hot water heater, and HVAC system installed in 2018, updated electrical, a newly remodeled bathroom and updated flooring adds to the home's appeal.Situated on a generous .55-acre corner lot, the property is fully fenced for security. A detached two-car garage provides ample storage space, while the expansive lot offers plenty of room for parking, RVs, trailers, toys, or even the creation of your own small farm. The recent upgrades will offer peace of mind for the new homeowner, and at this price, the condition can't be beat! Call today for more information and secure your opportunity to make this countryside retreat yours.
